{"id":2983,"date":"2024-03-08T15:17:58","date_gmt":"2024-03-08T08:17:58","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/captreonuisam.com\/?p=2983"},"modified":"2024-03-27T11:02:32","modified_gmt":"2024-03-27T04:02:32","slug":"hoi-cho-dem-tai-khu-du-lich-cap-treo-nui-sam","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/captreonuisam.com\/hoi-cho-dem-tai-khu-du-lich-cap-treo-nui-sam\/","title":{"rendered":"H\u1ed9i Ch\u1ee3 \u0110\u00eam &#8211; \u0110\u00eam vui nh\u01b0 h\u1ed9i t\u1ea1i Qu\u1ea3ng tr\u01b0\u1eddng khu du l\u1ecbch C\u00e1p treo N\u00fai Sam"},"content":{"rendered":"\n<p>Khi m\u00e0n \u0111\u00eam bu\u00f4ng xu\u1ed1ng l\u00e0&nbsp;l\u00fac c\u00e1c ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng h\u1ed9i ch\u1ee3 v\u1ec1 \u0111\u00eam l\u00ean ng\u00f4i,&nbsp;ch\u1edd \u0111\u00f3n du kh\u00e1ch t\u1ea1i&nbsp;qu\u1ea3ng tr\u01b0\u1eddng khu du l\u1ecbch C\u00e1p treo N\u00fai Sam, sau m\u1ed9t ng\u00e0y d\u00e0i th\u01b0\u1edfng ngo\u1ea1n du l\u1ecbch c\u00e1p treo, vi\u1ebfng B\u00e0 Ch\u00faa X\u1ee9, \u0111\u1ea3nh l\u1ec5 Ph\u1eadt,&#8230;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><a href=\"https:\/\/captreonuisam.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/03\/KDL-1.jpeg\"><img fetchpriority=\"high\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"697\" src=\"https:\/\/captreonuisam.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/03\/KDL-1-1024x697.jpeg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-2992\" title=\"\"><\/a><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p>H\u1ed9i ch\u1ee3 \u0111\u00eam t\u1ea1i n\u00fai Sam \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c d\u1ef1a tr\u00ean m\u00f4 h\u00ecnh h\u1ecdp ch\u1ee3 truy\u1ec1n th\u1ed1ng v\u1edbi c\u00e1c ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng gi\u1ea3i tr\u00ed, tr\u00f2 ch\u01a1i d\u00e2n gian th\u00e2n thu\u1ed9c, \u0111\u1eadm ch\u1ea5t mi\u1ec1n T\u00e2y, \u0111\u01b0a b\u00e0 con quay v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t g\u00f3c th\u1eddi thanh xu\u00e2n d\u00e2n d\u00e3, m\u1ed9c m\u1ea1c \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u00e1i hi\u1ec7n ngay t\u1ea1i khu\u00f4n vi\u00ean khu du l\u1ecbch. \u0110\u00e2y c\u0169ng l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng tr\u1ea3i nghi\u1ec7m \u0111\u1ed9c \u0111\u00e1o \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi kh\u00e1ch du l\u1ecbch n\u01b0\u1edbc ngo\u00e0i, \u0111\u1ebfn th\u0103m quan danh lam th\u1eafng c\u1ea3nh, t\u00ecm hi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 v\u0103n ho\u00e1 t\u00edn ng\u01b0\u1ee1ng \u1edf v\u00f9ng An Giang, Vi\u1ec7t Nam.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><a href=\"https:\/\/captreonuisam.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/03\/photo_6249221091658676736_w.jpg\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"1024\" src=\"https:\/\/captreonuisam.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/03\/photo_6249221091658676736_w-1024x1024.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-2993\" title=\"\" srcset=\"https:\/\/captreonuisam.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/03\/photo_6249221091658676736_w-1024x1024.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/captreonuisam.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/03\/photo_6249221091658676736_w-300x300.jpg 300w, https:\/\/captreonuisam.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/03\/photo_6249221091658676736_w-150x150.jpg 150w, https:\/\/captreonuisam.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/03\/photo_6249221091658676736_w-768x768.jpg 768w, https:\/\/captreonuisam.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/03\/photo_6249221091658676736_w-600x600.jpg 600w, https:\/\/captreonuisam.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/03\/photo_6249221091658676736_w-100x100.jpg 100w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" \/><\/a><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p>V\u1edbi s\u1ef1 k\u1ebft h\u1ee3p h\u00e0i h\u00f2a gi\u1eefa tr\u00f2 ch\u01a1i gi\u1ea3i tr\u00ed v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng gian vui nh\u1ed9n,&nbsp;ch\u1ee3&nbsp;\u0111\u00eam t\u1ea1i&nbsp;qu\u1ea3ng tr\u01b0\u1eddng khu du l\u1ecbch C\u00e1p treo N\u00fai Sam l\u00e0 n\u01a1i m\u00e0 du&nbsp;kh\u00e1ch&nbsp;c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u1eadn h\u01b0\u1edfng nh\u1eefng gi\u00e2y ph\u00fat th\u01b0 gi\u00e3n v\u00e0 tr\u00e0n \u0111\u1ea7y ni\u1ec1m vui. C\u00e1c ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng th\u00fa v\u1ecb nh\u01b0 b\u1eafn bong b\u00f3ng, v\u00f2ng quay may m\u1eafn \u0111ang ch\u1edd \u0111\u00f3n du kh\u00e1ch m\u1ed7i ng\u00e0y, th\u1eed v\u1eadn may v\u00e0 nh\u1eadn nh\u1eefng ph\u1ea7n th\u01b0\u1edfng h\u1ea5p&nbsp;d\u1eabn&nbsp;t\u1eeb nh\u1eefng tr\u00f2 ch\u01a1i d\u00e2n gian v\u00f9ng s\u00f4ng n\u01b0\u1edbc.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><a href=\"https:\/\/captreonuisam.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/03\/photo_6249221091658676734_w.jpg\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"1024\" src=\"https:\/\/captreonuisam.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/03\/photo_6249221091658676734_w-1024x1024.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-2994\" title=\"\" srcset=\"https:\/\/captreonuisam.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/03\/photo_6249221091658676734_w-1024x1024.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/captreonuisam.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/03\/photo_6249221091658676734_w-300x300.jpg 300w, https:\/\/captreonuisam.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/03\/photo_6249221091658676734_w-150x150.jpg 150w, https:\/\/captreonuisam.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/03\/photo_6249221091658676734_w-768x768.jpg 768w, https:\/\/captreonuisam.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/03\/photo_6249221091658676734_w-600x600.jpg 600w, https:\/\/captreonuisam.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/03\/photo_6249221091658676734_w-100x100.jpg 100w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" \/><\/a><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p>G\u00f3p&nbsp;ph\u1ea7n&nbsp;t\u1ea1o n\u00ean kh\u00f4ng kh\u00ed s\u1ed1ng \u0111\u1ed9ng v\u00e0 \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t&nbsp;c\u1ee7a du kh\u00e1ch d\u1ea1o ch\u1ee3 \u0111\u00eam, c\u00f4ng&nbsp;tr\u00ecnh nh\u1ea1c n\u01b0\u1edbc \u1edf khu v\u1ef1c trung t\u00e2m qu\u1ea3ng tr\u01b0\u1eddng&nbsp;k\u1ebft h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi \u00e2m&nbsp;nh\u1ea1c v\u00e0 \u00e1nh s\u00e1ng nh\u1ecbp nh\u00e0ng,&nbsp;h\u00f2a quy\u1ec7n l\u00e0m&nbsp;n\u00ean&nbsp;m\u1ed9t m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n \u0111\u1ea7y m\u00e0u s\u1eafc v\u00e0 s\u1ed1ng \u0111\u1ed9ng, mang \u0111\u1ebfn cho du kh\u00e1ch m\u1ed9t tr\u1ea3i nghi\u1ec7m tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi kh\u00f3 qu\u00ean.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><a href=\"https:\/\/captreonuisam.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/03\/z5224746240960_3a6385583545d5cc37119ea5a08844bd-2.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"2560\" height=\"1920\" src=\"https:\/\/captreonuisam.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/03\/z5224746240960_3a6385583545d5cc37119ea5a08844bd-2.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-2995\" title=\"\" srcset=\"https:\/\/captreonuisam.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/03\/z5224746240960_3a6385583545d5cc37119ea5a08844bd-2.jpg 2560w, https:\/\/captreonuisam.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/03\/z5224746240960_3a6385583545d5cc37119ea5a08844bd-2-1536x1152.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/captreonuisam.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/03\/z5224746240960_3a6385583545d5cc37119ea5a08844bd-2-2048x1536.jpg 2048w, https:\/\/captreonuisam.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/03\/z5224746240960_3a6385583545d5cc37119ea5a08844bd-2-200x150.jpg 200w, https:\/\/captreonuisam.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/03\/z5224746240960_3a6385583545d5cc37119ea5a08844bd-2-600x450.jpg 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 2560px) 100vw, 2560px\" \/><\/a><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p>H\u01a1n n\u1eefa, du kh\u00e1ch c\u00f2n c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i th\u01b0\u1edfng th\u1ee9c nh\u1eefng m\u00f3n \u0103n ngon t\u1ea1i nh\u00e0 h\u00e0ng h\u1ea3i s\u1ea3n ngo\u00e0i tr\u1eddi, v\u1eadn h\u00e0nh ph\u1ee5c v\u1ee5 24\/24. V\u1edbi kh\u00f4ng gian tho\u00e1ng \u0111\u00e3ng v\u00e0 nh\u1eefng m\u00f3n \u0103n t\u01b0\u01a1i ngon, b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 th\u01b0\u1edfng th\u1ee9c h\u1ea3i s\u1ea3n t\u01b0\u01a1i s\u1ed1ng v\u00e0 c\u00e1c m\u00f3n \u0103n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c&nbsp;chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb chu \u0111\u00e1o&nbsp;do&nbsp;ch\u00ednh tay c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ea7u b\u1ebfp d\u00e0y d\u1eb7n kinh nghi\u1ec7m \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1eeb khu du l\u1ecbch C\u00e1p treo N\u00fai Sam.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Ngo\u00e0i ra, du kh\u00e1ch c\u00f2n c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i th\u1eafng&nbsp;nh\u1eefng ph\u1ea7n qu\u00e0 gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb trong&nbsp;ch\u01b0\u01a1ng tr\u00ecnh L\u00f4 T\u00f4 Show duy nh\u1ea5t&nbsp;\u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ea5p ph\u00e9p ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng&nbsp;t\u1ea1i Ch\u00e2u \u0110\u1ed1c, An Giang. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t s\u1ef1 ki\u1ec7n mang t\u00ednh bi\u1ec3u t\u01b0\u1ee3ng, n\u01a1i m\u00e0 du&nbsp;kh\u00e1ch&nbsp;c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n&nbsp;s\u1ef1&nbsp;may m\u1eafn&nbsp;c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>H\u1ed9i Ch\u1ee3 \u0110\u00eam t\u1ea1i\u00a0qu\u1ea3ng tr\u01b0\u1eddng khu du l\u1ecbch C\u00e1p treo N\u00fai Sam l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t tr\u1ea3i nghi\u1ec7m tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi cho du kh\u00e1ch mu\u1ed1n th\u01b0 gi\u00e3n v\u00e0 kh\u00e1m ph\u00e1 v\u0103n h\u00f3a d\u00e2n gian\u00a0mi\u1ec1n T\u00e2y. H\u00e3y \u0111\u1ebfn Khu\u00a0du l\u1ecbch C\u00e1p treo N\u00fai Sam \u0111\u1ec3\u00a0tr\u1ea3i\u00a0nghi\u1ec7m tr\u1ecdn v\u1eb9n chuy\u1ebfn h\u00e0nh tr\u00ecnh v\u00e0 tham gia\u00a0\u0111\u00eam ch\u1ee3\u00a0vui nh\u01b0 h\u1ed9i, ng\u1eafm nh\u00ecn c\u1ea3nh quan \u0111\u1eb9p v\u00e0 th\u1eed nh\u1eefng ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng \u0111\u1eb7c s\u1eafc t\u1ea1i\u00a0\u0111\u00e2y &#8211;\u00a0m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec3m \u0111\u1ebfn h\u1ea5p d\u1eabn nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a An Giang.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>\u0110\u1ec3 bi\u1ebft th\u00eam th\u00f4ng tin chi ti\u1ebft, vui l\u00f2ng li\u00ean h\u1ec7 v\u1edbi ch\u00fang t\u00f4i<strong>\u00a0<\/strong>\u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u01b0 v\u1ea5n v\u1ec1 l\u1ed9 tr\u00ecnh tham quan, c\u00e1c \u01b0u \u0111\u00e3i v\u00e0 khuy\u1ebfn m\u00e3i trong th\u1eddi gian s\u1edbm nh\u1ea5t.<\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Khi m\u00e0n \u0111\u00eam bu\u00f4ng xu\u1ed1ng l\u00e0&nbsp;l\u00fac c\u00e1c ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng h\u1ed9i ch\u1ee3 v\u1ec1 \u0111\u00eam l\u00ean ng\u00f4i,&nbsp;ch\u1edd \u0111\u00f3n du kh\u00e1ch t\u1ea1i&nbsp;qu\u1ea3ng tr\u01b0\u1eddng khu du l\u1ecbch C\u00e1p treo N\u00fai Sam, sau m\u1ed9t ng\u00e0y d\u00e0i th\u01b0\u1edfng ngo\u1ea1n du l\u1ecbch c\u00e1p treo, vi\u1ebfng B\u00e0 Ch\u00faa X\u1ee9, \u0111\u1ea3nh l\u1ec5 Ph\u1eadt,&#8230; H\u1ed9i ch\u1ee3 \u0111\u00eam t\u1ea1i n\u00fai Sam \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c d\u1ef1a tr\u00ean [&hellip;]<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":3,"featured_media":0,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"footnotes":""},"categories":[1],"tags":[129,130],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/captreonuisam.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/2983"}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/captreonuisam.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/captreonuisam.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/captreonuisam.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/3"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/captreonuisam.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=2983"}],"version-history":[{"count":1,"href":"https:\/\/captreonuisam.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/2983\/revisions"}],"predecessor-version":[{"id":2996,"href":"https:\/\/captreonuisam.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/2983\/revisions\/2996"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/captreonuisam.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=2983"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/captreonuisam.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/categories?post=2983"},{"taxonomy":"post_tag","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/captreonuisam.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/tags?post=2983"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https:\/\/api.w.org\/{rel}","templated":true}]}}